        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3>Tenor 12 Bulan</h3>
          <p><strong>Plafond Rp. 2 jt</strong>: Rp. 210.666</p>
          <p><strong>Plafond Rp. 5 jt</strong>: Rp. 526.666</p>
          <p><strong>Plafond Rp. 8 jt</strong>: Rp. 842.666</p>
          <p><strong>Plafond Rp. 10 jt</strong>: Rp. 1.053.333</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
